WEBVTT

00:01:58.214 --> 00:02:00.658
O makwa n'abu m dimkpa Africa?

00:02:00.682 --> 00:02:01.696
(Ochi)

00:02:01.720 --> 00:02:03.891
Dika Okonkwo, n'ime "Things Fall Apart,"

00:02:03.891 --> 00:02:08.356
Anyi bu umu nwoke Africa 
anaghi ekwuputa ihe na-akpagbu anyi

00:02:08.661 --> 00:02:10.662
Anyi na-e gbokwa mkpa anyi 
n'onwe anyi

00:02:10.686 --> 00:02:12.229
(Iku aka)

00:02:13.181 --> 00:02:15.180
Anyi na-e gbokwa mkpa anyi 
n'onwe anyi.

00:02:15.204 --> 00:02:19.975
A kporo m nwanne m nwoke, 
ma chikwa ochi megide ndi oyibo--

00:02:19.999 --> 00:02:21.856
na kwa oria di iche iche ha na-aya--

00:02:21.880 --> 00:02:25.118
nchegbu, na kwa ihe ndi ozo.

00:02:26.060 --> 00:02:28.491
Site n'ozuzu m nwetara n'West Africa,
O bu onye ara

00:02:28.515 --> 00:02:32.896
bu isi ruru unyi, gbakwara oto a kpaghari
